# Clara visual design — Cycladic Mediterranean

**Direction:** Stark white/plaster neutrals, **grove green** primary (`#3D5A2A`), **lemon yellow** accent (`#D4B800`) **only** for exam countdown UI and hours progress bars / “Log hours” actions. **Cormorant Garamond** for wordmark, page titles (h1), and metric numerals. **Inter** for all other UI. **No** border-radius except **2px** on quiz/study answer bubbles only. **No** shadows or gradients; **1px** `clara-border` dividers.

## Tokens (`tailwind.config.ts` → `clara-*`)

| Token | Hex | Role |
|----|-----|---|
| `bg` | `#FFFFFF` | Page background |
| `surface` | `#FAFAF8` | Sidebar, secondary panels |
| `tint` | `#F0F5EC` | Active nav wash, good-score badges |
| `border` | `#E8E8E0` | Dividers, outlines |
| `primary` | `#3D5A2A` | CTAs, active nav text, links, fills |
| `primary-hover` | `#324A22` | Primary hover |
| `accent` | `#D4B800` | Exam badge, hours bars, Log hours buttons only |
| `deep` | `#1A1A14` | Body and headings |
| `muted` | `#AAAAAA` | Secondary labels |
| `danger` | `#B84820` | Weak / low scores |
| `danger-bg` | `#FFF0E8` | Weak badge background |
| `exam` | `#FFFBE8` | Exam countdown metric cell |

## Typography

- **Cormorant Garamond** (`font-cormorant`): wordmark “Clara”, dashboard **h1** / page titles, large **metric values**.
- **Inter** (`font-sans`): navigation, labels, buttons, inputs, body.

## Buttons (`Button.tsx`)

- **primary** — green fill, white label, uppercase tracking.
- **ghost** — white fill, green border + text.
- **accent** — lemon fill, deep text (Log hours only).

## Badges (`Badge.tsx`)

- **green / blue** — `tint` + `primary` text (good / info).
- **yellow** — white + border (neutral caution).
- **red** — `danger-bg` + `danger` text (weak).

## Do / don’t

- **Do** use `gap-px` + `bg-clara-border` grids for metric cells; `1px` borders for sections.
- **Don’t** use `box-shadow`, gradients, or **accent** color outside exam + hours affordances.
